## Proposed Execution Plan

### Sprint 1: Auth & Node Token Flow (Foundation for everything else)
1. Create `POST /api/v1/nodes/me/{node_id}/token` ‚Äî generates a node-scoped JWT
2. Update `POST /nodes/register` response to include a `node_token` field
3. Create `app/services/billing_service.py` with chunk cost calculation
4. Create `app/utils/gamification.py` with rank tiers + streak tracking

### Sprint 2: Web Contributor Pages
5. Build `/contributor` page ‚Äî node list, status, earnings
6. Build `/contributor/register` page ‚Äî register node, show UUID + token
7. Build `/contributor/leaderboard` page 
8. Wire Dashboard stats to real API data (`GPU Hours`, `Credits`)
9. Fix framer-motion/dropzone type conflict in Submit page

### Sprint 3: Server Billing & Leaderboard
10. Create `GET /api/v1/leaderboard` endpoint
11. Wire `BillingService` into the chunk completion flow in `matcher.py`
12. Fill the `total_gpu_hours_today` TODO in `nodes.py`
13. Add `GET /api/v1/nodes/me/{node_id}/history` endpoint for Tauri

### Sprint 4: Tauri Auth & Contributor UX
14. Build a **Setup/Login screen** in the Tauri React frontend
15. Add token persistence using Tauri's filesystem API (stored in app data)
16. Build **History page** in Tauri
17. Build **Earnings panel** with real data in Tauri Dashboard
18. Wire WebSocket auth to use the stored node JWT instead of `internal_node`

